<del rend="strikethrough"> aws d </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488341360_5400">
<del rend="strikethrough">teydingten / vnd daʒ du der </del> komen / der du genüſʒt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488353001_5410">daʒ du aws <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> vanknüʒʒ komſt / 
<del rend="strikethrough">mit redlichen teydingen </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488368253_5423">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſölichen teydingen / daʒ </del> vnd geteydingt würdſt / . vnd </ab>
