<ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488460630_5531">den heiligen geſworn vnd dich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>punden</expan> haſt / . vnd dein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_r2l45">frewnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">mit </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488399712_5461">cʒü </ab></add> dir geſworn / . vnd du vnd ſie güt beſıgelt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488464400_5536">briefe <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / die 
<add><ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488713115_5836">briefe vnd </ab><ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488715495_5841">vrkünde </ab></add> wir <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> dir vnd deinen frewnden </ab>
