<ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488675508_5803">wollen wir dir 
<add><ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488718397_5846"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>deine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488720695_5851"><expan>ſcheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488723025_5856">mit <expan>deıne<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488725315_5861"><expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalte </ab></add> ob du cʒü vns cʒe ſprechen heſt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> eins </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488679924_5808"><expan>frewntlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> rechten ſeın / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ob du cʒü Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_line_1576488684554_5813">cʒeſprechen heſt / frewntlıchs <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> helffen / alles an </ab>
